text: Basket Racing Club Luxembourg (also Racing Luxembourg) is a Luxembourgish professional basketball club. The club has won the national championship 3 times, along with 1 Luxembourg Cup. == Honours == ===Luxembourgian League=== * Winners (3): 1966-67, 1997–98, 1999-00 ===Luxembourgian Cup=== * Winners (1): 2000-01 == External links == * Basket Racing Club Luxembourg official site Category:Basketball teams in Luxembourg
title: Basket Racing Club Luxembourg
